request.description:
### Register User

This endpoint is used to register a new user.

#### Request Body

- `profileIcon` (string): Unique identifier referencing a profile Bitmoji.

- `name` (string): The user's full name.

- `annonymousName` (string): A randomly generated username.

- `email` (string): The user's email address.

- `phoneNumber` (string): The user's phone number.

- `phoneNote` (string): Additional note about the phone number.

- `password` (string): The user's chosen password.

- `deviceType` (string): The type of device (android/ios).

- `deviceId` (string): The device ID from Firebase FCM.

- `timezone` (string): The user's timezone.


#### Response (JSON Schema)

``` json
{
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
        "message": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "data": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
                "basicInfo": {
                    "type": "object",
                    "properties": {
                        "profileIcon": {
                            "type": "string"
                        },
                        "name": {
                            "type": "string"
                        },
                        "annonymousName": {
                            "type": "string"
                        },
                        "email": {
                            "type": "string"
                        },
                        "phoneNumber": {
                            "type": "string"
                        },
                        "phoneNote": {
                            "type": "string"
                        }
                    }
                },
                "accountState": {
                    "type": "object",
                    "properties": {
                        "userType": {
                            "type": "string"
                        },
                        "status": {
                            "type": "string"
                        },
                        "verificationStatus": {
                            "type": "string"
                        }
                    }
                },
                "profileCompletionStatus": {
                    "type": "object",
                    "properties": {
                        "personalDetails": {
                            "type": "boolean"
                        },
                        "pregnancyDetails": {
                            "type": "boolean"
                        },
                        "lossDetails": {
                            "type": "boolean"
                        },
                        "healingDetails": {
                            "type": "boolean"
                        }
                    }
                },
                "metadata": {
                    "type": "object",
                    "properties": {
                        "_id": {
                            "type": "string"
                        },
                        "timezone": {
                            "type": "string"
                        },
                        "createdAt": {
                            "type": "string"
                        },
                        "updatedAt": {
                            "type": "string"
                        },
                        "__v": {
                            "type": "integer"
                        }
                    }
                },
                "otpInfo": {
                    "type": "object",
                    "properties": {
                        "otp": {
                            "type": "string"
                        },
                        "otpUsed": {
                            "type": "boolean"
                        },
                        "otpExpires": {
                            "type": "string"
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    }
}

